This version of Magico is the first version that adds initial FreeBSD support.

### Changes

This release contains a variety of changes, including, but not limited to:

- `[+]` Added initial FreeBSD support

Review the commit history if you want to get a deep insight about the changes.

### Feedback?

If you have issues with this version, report to us by [making a new issue ticket](https://github.com/Aptivi/Magico/issues/new).

